<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Gegin</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-19 23:44:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I must admit, I owned the lists of all the weapons dropped<BR>
in SolA, and didn't see this one listed until I picked up<BR>
loot.  Being a 36 ranger, I find it easy to simply run past<BR>
the mobs on the way to this spawn, the PH is the mob inside<BR>
the door at the top of the stairs from the foremans' room.<BR>
I sat and killed the two spawns (predator/foreman) for <BR>
nearly 6hrs..all green but I did receive exp from 1 maybe 2<BR>
of the predators.  I had been in the hall with a 44 warrior,<BR>
(pretending I was a healer ;).  Within an hour he had left <BR>
for the SolB King's room and I kept the spawn solo.  Within<BR>
4 hours, this was my total loot:<BR>
<BR>
4 pairs of Kobold Hide boots <BR>
1 Foreman's Tunic (given to the warrior along w/pr. boots)<BR>
1 Obisidian Shard (Kobo also had the boots)<BR>
1 Tattered Gnomes Cloak (some gnomie quest)<BR>
and get this...<BR>
<BR>
2 Obsidian Scimitars(on back to back spawns of the foreman!)<BR>
<BR>
and nearly 150pp from sales of FS weapons and loot<BR>
<BR>
Well worth my time and effort...one night of exp lost...bah!<BR>
<BR>
Good Luck all!  (btw 18 min spawn rate is correct, but I <BR>
killed the Kobo roughly once every hour, just stay in the<BR>
hall, check on the Foreman, who's room must be cleared to <BR>
spawn him regularly... listen for that howl and you're in!;)<BR>
<BR>
Gegin Thunderblade<BR>
36th Ranger of Prexus</font></td></tr></table>
